title: Cross Country Teams Perform Well at Open New England's (Bowdoin College Athletics)
text: ( Source : Bowdoin College Athletics ) BOSTON, Mass. - The Bowdoin College cross country teams raced well at the 2015 Open New England Championship Saturday at Franklin Park . The Polar Bear men finished 21st overall while the women took 23rd
